      <title>泰晤士水务公司债务被削减至垃圾处理费，努力避免罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/moody-s-cuts-thames-water-s-highest-ranked-bonds-to-junk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司请求监管机构帮助其避免巨额罚款，此前穆迪将其最优先债务评级下调为垃圾债，这进一步加大了英国最大供水商的财务压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/moody-s-cuts-thames-water-s-highest-ranked-bonds-to-junk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 11:29:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
